<br>
I can't knock them for doing what they did, because some one would have done it at some point in time anyways.<br>
<br>
What if everyone in the game started a new character on Xev because they wanted to see the sleeper sleeping, is that grounds to pretty much *order* guilds to not wake him?  I think not.<br>
<br>
That is my point.  We choose the server we play on, and if we don't like it, we leave and start on another one.  If people don't like that, they too bad.  It's the truth and nothing can change that.<br>
<br>
Meanwhile, there is a thing called Character Transfer for all the people who want to see the sleeper sleep.  Move to Kane Bayle.  It's FFA and wayyyyyyyyyy too underpopulated.  Your entire guild can move there and they'll still have room for 10 more.  The people are willing to share there.  In fact, here is a post from our board about this board and what you people are saying about Hawkethorne, I'll even post the link to the page so you don't think I'm lying, and no I didn't post it.  My name is the same across all these EZBoards...<br>
