<br>
Believe me, it actually kinda sucks at the really high levels (60+).  There's basically nothing more in the game to do other than raid, and that's pretty sad.  No more quests, since better gear drops on a daily basis.  It's sad but true, and look at the result of it.  1 group of people *fucking it up* for everyone else.  That's what makes this game sucks, but keeps some of us coming back everyday for more.<br>
<br>
These boards are just a way to have fun.  Really, I would never stand in anyone's face and tell them the things that I write on this board.  The only reason why people write them is because some people seem to take it a bit too seriously and react just the way others want them too.<br>
<br>
Like I said, if you really wanna see the sleeper, transfer to KB.  The sleeper there is still sleeping and even though there are the occassional assholes, everyone knows who they are because the population is so small.  If you do transfer, you shouldn't have a problem fitting yourself into full Elysian gear, especially if you meet me.  I'm tired of PoP exp anyways and despite what my image on these rant boards may be, I'm quite the giving type.<br>
<br>
Hell, I gave away over 20k gear to a level 1 enchanter the other day just becuase I didn't feel like logging to transfer it to my main from my level 33 mage alt there.<br>
